  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Laparoscopic sentinel lymph node biopsy and stomach preserving surgery in ealry gastric
      cancer is less invasive method which can increase quality of life. Multicenter phase III
      trial is requred to validate this method. In this study all items which are necessary for
      laparoscopic sentinel lymph node biopsy are identified according to checklist and evaluated
      the performance completement.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
